                     for acquiring charisma (fols. 15r-45r), incomplete (cp. EMML nos. 1380,
                     3508)&#xD; III) Directives for reading the sacred books (?) (fols.
                     47r-51v)&#xD; IV) Malkǝʾa Fānuʾel “Image of Phanuʾel” (fols. 55r-83v),
                     incomplete (the final fols. are missing) (ChRep p. 202, no. 166)&#xD; &#xD;
